Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二堂課  \NTHE  自習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭•剪刀•布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才不是說明了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏的人要打對方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分哦  好過分的態度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上比打我還過分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？  就像剛才說明的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸的話就防御  贏的話就打人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}擊碎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是現在啦  為什麼現在打呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我剛才贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是現在  那是剛才啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在當下  活在當下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是那樣的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後出布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂出喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就重新來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭•剪刀•布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁為零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丑啊  就像小丑一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神受到打擊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等下  麻衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你要…幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挖到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  這一定是轉世再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個放這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得她很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那種東西怎樣都好  來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  石頭•剪刀•布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻衣  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}決定一擊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是石剪布啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼如此殘忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算不算  不准出石剪布啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有不准用佛像打人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}蓋斯科因！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  來吧  先出石頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭•剪刀•布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是  就是那樣哦  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做還是做得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  再來再來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  先出石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOD  IS  DEAD！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  為什麼又要打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  剛才不是玩得很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是覺得不想玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我看看彌勒菩薩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我去圖書館還書了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好地看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.63,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N21
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:57.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}冰箱上：不可以吃太多冰淇淋和果汁哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼名乃的不倒翁只有一隻眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  要是博士把眼睛畫上去的話  說不定會表揚我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃也許會說「你吃一堆點心也沒關係哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像有點畫歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是名乃的  怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也許會惹她生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時不准博士吃零食！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  這樣畫  這樣畫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本  怎麼辦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼  你這傢伙都幹了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那小姑娘的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它沒有眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊  你就照我說的試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先開溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  阪本先生你要出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要選新借的書所以回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  你那肚子是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  誒嘿嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是誒嘿嘿啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  沒有那種可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要生了啦！  我要生了  我要生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:10.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那個  你這是在玩什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  名乃的弟弟要誕生啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:29.95,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,240)\fad(600,0)}錢\N仙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩錢仙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美緒居然不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我稍微說明一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在正中畫一個鳥居
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後寫上「是」與「否」和五十音圖  就準備這樣的一張紙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:55.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}錢仙又叫狐狗狸，油炸豆腐據說是其喜歡的食物。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然根據地域不同  也有說在紙上寫上油炸豆腐會比較好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就按最簡單的來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能讓錢仙進來  要打開北邊的門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把這枚10円硬幣放在這個鳥居的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起壓住硬幣  然後問想問的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人的秘密之類的  喜歡的人的事情之類的  苦惱著的事情之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話明明什麼都沒做  10円硬幣一下子動了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢仙就會做出回答哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先不能一個人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能以開玩笑的心態去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則會被低級靈附身的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  在途中停止的話也會被附身的  要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種感覺  還算是蠻危險的遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  總之開始玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:09.22,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N22
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天的課就到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要進行小考  大家回去要好好學習哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  推遲啦推遲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無論怎麼推遲結果都是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  相生同學  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些想問的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  是關於前一陣小考的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這題是FLY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是問答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裡指勇者鬥惡龍裡面的消失咒「ニフラム」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個看上去好像被下了消失咒的是老師畫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得在考試中加入圖片能讓考試變得更加靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師畫的畫真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我不是很擅長畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題目很難看懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼老師  下次就用我畫的畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會畫得超帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說聽說我  我畫的畫會出在小考上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師說了「會用我畫的畫」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒你現在畫的話也許也會出在卷子上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你說會出  那也有不會出的可能性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  你不畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就算了  不必了  我還得去還這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  那我就畫一個超帥的帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的好帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學真會畫畫呢  佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:18:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  其實我就是畫得…那麼好啦  開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一下畫的名字叫做「梅雨下的喬治」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  感覺更加帥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫帥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你們兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般被稱作帥的應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厲害  好像漫畫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長野原同學  你有在畫漫畫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  嘛  只是稍微畫畫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  下次讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看  讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我畫的比你更帥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這不是抄襲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這可不是抄襲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抄襲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是名為抄襲的致敬！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這根本就是承認了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都說帥的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這樣畫的話怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種充滿知性的冷酷形象  無論在哪個時代都是女性憧憬的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他視力不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是戴上隱形眼鏡的話或許更好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙簡直完全不懂嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣畫！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡戴到耳朵下面了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這也是抄襲我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖嘖  這可是太陽眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒有下限嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這樣畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從出門迎接到紅茶服務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你大小姐般的享受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受大吉嶺紅茶的魔力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又是眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我不是很懂這方面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼呼  不聽隱形眼鏡的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒你根本就不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  真正的帥指的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唰唰唰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮在空中！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子在開動！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像很快  好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說帥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說帥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說帥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常識上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以常識來考慮的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說帥的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個樣子的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:17.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}15:40  1-Q講台前  長野原美緒  擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句話時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊聽著爵士樂一邊畫了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老濕  早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是老濕啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我現在開始分發早上的小考試卷  請傳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是失敗  畫畫這件事本來我想保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然畫出了那樣的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  嘛  儘管我暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只畫到了那種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是不幸中之萬幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能不去想最壞的狀況了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這兩三天就得接受祐子的嘲笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  我得振作  繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒老濕快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  考試開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒老濕～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.86,0:24:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  咻  啊噠噠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  初次見面  我是擬聲詞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕嚕嚕嚕嚕是不想說的日語呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是什麼日語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的日常是第六話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
